      },
      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws and 5.5 mm Ti-6Al-4V rods. Components drawn from two separate manufacturing lots to assess inter-lot variability. Sample traceability documented in Sample Receipt and Inspection Report SRIR-2024-007. Testing conducted across two independent laboratories (FDA OSEL and DePuy Synthes R&D) to assess inter-laboratory reproducibility."
