        "description": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions, set-screw torque) must be set to values measured directly from the test articles used in bench testing, not nominal design values. Gradation 2 minimum; Gradation 3 achieved by formal equivalency table with tolerance analysis."
