        "name": "Output comparison acceptance criteria — E/uval < 1.96 and |QoI difference| < 10%",
        "description": "Validation metric: E/uval < 1.96 (95% confidence interval) for all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm), where E is the mean prediction error and uval is the combined experimental and model uncertainty. Additionally, the mean absolute percentage error must be < 10% for each QoI."
